    <h2><span class="section-num">3.</span> Service Description</h2>
    <p>GOPulse is a mobile application developed by NorthStack Labs Inc. that provides GO Transit train tracking, departure information, journey planning, service alerts, and departure notifications. GOPulse is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Metrolinx, GO Transit, or any government agency. Transit data is sourced from publicly available Metrolinx Open Data APIs. Map services are provided by Google Maps. The App relies on third-party services for backend infrastructure, push notifications, subscription management, and error monitoring.</p>
