    <p>GOPulse is an independent information tool and does not provide official transit advice or services. The App is not a substitute for official GO Transit communications and should not be used as the sole basis for time-critical travel decisions. For safety-critical or time-sensitive travel plans, always verify schedules and service status directly with GO Transit (gotransit.com or the GO Transit customer service line). NorthStack Labs Inc. assumes no responsibility for decisions made based solely on information displayed in the App.</p>
