&bull; Subscription length: GO Pulse+ is offered as a monthly or annual auto-renewable subscription.
&bull; Free trial: New subscribers may be eligible for a 7-day free trial. At the end of the trial period, your subscription will automatically convert to a paid subscription unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the trial ends.
&bull; Billing: Payment is charged to your Apple ID or Google Play account at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period.
&bull; Price: The subscription price is displayed on the purchase screen. Prices may vary by region and are subject to change.
&bull; Cancellation: You may cancel your subscription at any time through your device's subscription settings (Settings &gt; Apple ID &gt; Subscriptions on iOS, or Google Play Store &gt; Subscriptions on Android). Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. No refunds are provided for partial periods.
&bull; Features: GO Pulse+ provides access to premium features as described on the subscription purchase screen. Feature availability may change over time.
&bull; Refunds: Refund requests are handled by Apple (App Store) or Google (Play Store) in accordance with their respective refund policies.</p>
